    "description": "VybssProfileKeys — Social trading keys with bonding curve (Friend.tech style)\nBuy/sell keys of any creator. Price follows bonding curve: price = supply² * 1e8 / 16000.\n5% creator royalty + 5% protocol fee on every trade.",
